{"tid":343950,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分左手幾耐鍾意第二個先正常","createTime":"2017-08-02T01:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T08:50:29.000Z","uid":32835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56e576018626a9b41583a093eebfdf4ac34e91dd","tid":343950,"uid":32835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T01:49:07.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n<br />\n係咪一定要等好耐，係咪一定唔可以分左即刻鍾意第二個。<br />\n係咪一定會俾人話..."},{"pid":"16bd679231ab900bc8abdfc71cc06d5c7cf0445a","tid":343950,"uid":27777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T01:50:05.000Z","msg":"唔係 即刻都得"},{"pid":"e5d2173ff986e151bfdc37c7bd3a92dfc1ff010c","tid":343950,"uid":84138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T01:50:52.000Z","msg":"咁快就中意未必係真 只不過係想揾人陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7579434823132a9af4244f3cfda7b517cd60c087","tid":343950,"uid":32835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T01:53:21.000Z","msg":"會唔會俾人話唔係認真對第二個，又或者係想溝第二個先同第一個分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e3f636ecc721d78041d29c0518736b253e7ef2","tid":343950,"uid":27777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T01:54:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會俾人話唔係認真對第二個，又或者係想溝第二個先同第一個分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鐘意人就去啦 諗咁多做乜撚"},{"pid":"3b82f661bf0a4688369666f23e3156e1d5be0c5d","tid":343950,"uid":45565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:12:17.000Z","msg":"睇人 <br />\n我係好易鐘意人<br />\n相處一陣就已經可以好有好感<br />\n試過被分手2星期到就鐘意左第個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be0c0c77f8e44771dcdee12ad89e5d3a0cbe5e3","tid":343950,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:07:40.000Z","msg":"分手前"},{"pid":"a75e8102b3bf47459ccf9252b58d8d86f251d908","tid":343950,"uid":107775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T04:11:13.000Z","msg":"其實係分完即刻都得<br />\n但係之前識條臭西 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同我散完過兩個禮拜就同左第二條仔一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要話我知係講笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後同第二個散左一個月都未夠<br />\n又同第三個一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢啲女真係臭西雞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我唔在意佢同邊個一齊<br />\n但係我介意佢扮撚曬自己好專一咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"052d1cba59acc2def12c101900c8ed74f6fcb7b6","tid":343950,"uid":96979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T08:41:25.000Z","msg":"或者之前果個水泡嚟"},{"pid":"b271fbcd6231a1d9bbe04109a272ec1da0528f1b","tid":343950,"uid":96157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T08:50:29.000Z","msg":"鍾意咪鍾意囉<br />\n唔通人地話你太快唔正常你就即刻變唔鍾意咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正唔正常有咩所謂<br />\n最緊要拍拖拍得開心<br />\n理得人地講咩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}